    "beat_id": "ch-001-jammed-gear-beat-001-mira-climbs-tower-stairs-noting",
    "beat_description": "Mira climbs the tower stairs, noting the unusual quiet of the water wheel. She unlocks the gear room and finds the main gear jammed with a broken spoke lodged in the teeth.",
    "planned_characters": [
      "Mira Vale"
